Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Tennessee jails crisis
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xp7s
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 Nov 1985
Tennessee judge demands that state resolves prison overcrowding so he can continue sentencing. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less